Package: scReportEnrichment
Type: Package
Title: Single-Cell Functional Enrichment Interactive HTML Report
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Kee-gong Karios",
                  family = "Park",
                  email = "karioslion0517@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate self-contained interactive HTML reports from pre-computed
    ORA (Over-Representation Analysis) functional enrichment results. Accepts
    generic data.frames or clusterProfiler enrichResult objects and produces a
    styled report with overview cards, dot plots, bar plots, searchable term
    tables, and term detail panels. Part of the scReport ecosystem alongside
    scReportLite, scReportComposition, and scReportDE.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    plotly
Suggests:
    clusterProfiler,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.0
